        "text": "This version of the term does not originate from psychology, but from cybernetics. However, it can also be interpreted psychologically. For the general term see, for example, Heinz von Foerster, Observing Systems, Seaside Ca1. 1981; Niklas Luhmann et a1., Beobachter: Konvergenz der Erkenntnistheorien?, Munich 1990; Niklas Luhmann, Die Wissenschaft der Gesellschaft, Frankfurt 1990, p. 68 ff. Vg1. also Francesco Pardi, L'osservabilita dell'agire sociale, Milano 1985, with reference to the earlier literature."
